original:
"The Cocaine God"
It was the year 1985 when the small town of Santa Maria del Sol found itself under the oppressive rule of one man - the Cocaine God. His real name had long been forgotten; instead, people whispered his infamous nickname in hushed tones, afraid even the mention of his name would bring about their doom. He had built his empire on the white powder that left lives shattered and dream
